Sixshot/Dark One:




Sixshot pulled up, easily dodging whatever it was that was thrown at him.  He 
laughed, he was now just a tad bit ahead of the Maximals.  He slowled down 
until he got to a slow enough velocity, and send all power into his engines.  
He turned, Windlord now coming into sight since he/she was maintaining her 
speed and trying to get faster.

He fired off 25 rapid laser blasts at the moving form, and two 
energy-signature seeking missiles at Windlord.

---

Dark One knew what Sixshot was doing, it was a good tactical maneuver in his 
opinion.  He launched off two energy-signature seeking missiles at Warlord 
from behind.  He then fired ten rapid laser blasts from the laser weaponry in 
the cone of his ship at Angel Prime.
